---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Restaurant Marketing in Vaughan | Toronto Restaurant Growth"
  description="Vaughan restaurant marketing — upscale dining, Italian corridor, and Middle Eastern cuisine in one of Ontario's wealthiest suburbs. We help Vaughan restaurants rank on Google."
>

  <main style="padding-top: 80px;">

    <nav style="padding: 16px 24px; background: #f5f5f0; font-size: 0.85rem;" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/" style="color: #E85D04; text-decoration: none;">Home</a>
      <span style="color: #666; margin: 0 8px;">›</span>
      <a href="/locations/" style="color: #E85D04; text-decoration: none;">Locations</a>
      <span style="color: #666; margin: 0 8px;">›</span>
      Restaurant Marketing Vaughan
    </nav>

    <section style="background: #1a1a1a; color: #fff; padding: 100px 24px 80px; text-align: center;">
      <div style="max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <p style="text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; font-size: 0.78rem; color: #E85D04; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px;">Vaughan, Ontario</p>
        <h1 style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 4rem); color: #fff; margin-bottom: 20px;">Restaurant Marketing in Vaughan</h1>
        <p style="font-size: 1.2rem; color: #ccc; max-width: 620px; margin: 0 auto 36px;">
          Vaughan's dining market is upscale, multicultural, and growing fast around the VMC. Italian, Middle Eastern, and international concepts are competing for a customer base with high disposable income and high expectations. Is your restaurant winning?
        </p>
        <a href="/contact/" style="display: inline-block; background: #E85D04; color: #fff; padding: 16px 36px; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem;">Book a Free Google Audit</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section style="background: #fff; padding: 72px 24px;">
      <div style="max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <p style="text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; font-size: 0.78rem; color: #E85D04; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px;">The Local Food Scene</p>
        <h2 style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.6rem); margin-bottom: 20px;">Vaughan: Upscale Dining Meets Multicultural Community</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: #333;">
          Vaughan's Italian-Canadian community has shaped the city's restaurant culture for decades — the Woodbridge area has one of the most concentrated populations of Italian-Canadian families in North America, and the restaurants here reflect that heritage. Traditional Italian trattorias, modern Italian-fusion concepts, and the kind of Sunday-lunch culture that keeps regulars coming back for decades.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: #333;">
          But Vaughan's dining scene has diversified dramatically over the past decade. The VMC (Vaughan Metropolitan Centre) development has brought new density, younger demographics, and an appetite for everything from Persian and Lebanese to modern Canadian fine dining. Rutherford Road has become a destination corridor for families across York Region.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-bottom: 16px; color: #333;">
          Vaughan's customers have high household incomes and high dining frequency. They choose restaurants based on online research — reviews, Google Maps positioning, and social media presence. Getting your digital presence right in Vaughan is not optional. It's table stakes.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section style="background: #f5f5f0; padding: 72px 24px;">
      <div style="max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <p style="text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; font-size: 0.78rem; color: #E85D04; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px;">What We Do</p>
        <h2 style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.6rem); margin-bottom: 20px;">What We Do For Vaughan Restaurants</h2>
        <ul style="list-style: none; margin-top: 28px;">
          <li style="padding: 14px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0d8; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px;">
            <span style="color: #E85D04; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px;">→</span>
            <span style="color: #333;"><strong>Premium Market Positioning:</strong> Vaughan's customers expect polished digital presence. We build Google profiles, websites, and social accounts that match the quality of your food and signal to your target customer that you're the right choice.</span>
          </li>
          <li style="padding: 14px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0d8; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px;">
            <span style="color: #E85D04; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px;">→</span>
            <span style="color: #333;"><strong>VMC and Woodbridge SEO:</strong> We target the specific area searches Vaughan customers use — from Woodbridge Italian dining to VMC restaurant searches to Rutherford Road corridors.</span>
          </li>
          <li style="padding: 14px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0d8; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px;">
            <span style="color: #E85D04; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px;">→</span>
            <span style="color: #333;"><strong>Family Dining Focus:</strong> Vaughan has one of the highest proportions of family dining occasions in the GTA. Content and promotions that speak to family gatherings, Sunday dinners, and celebration meals perform exceptionally in this market.</span>
          </li>
          <li style="padding: 14px 0; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px;">
            <span style="color: #E85D04; font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px;">→</span>
            <span style="color: #333;"><strong>Review and Reputation Management:</strong> High-income diners leave detailed reviews and read them carefully. We manage your reputation across Google, Yelp, and TripAdvisor to ensure your online presence reflects the quality of your restaurant.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section style="background: #f5f5f0; padding: 72px 24px;">
      <div style="max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <p style="text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.12em; font-size: 0.78rem; color: #E85D04; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px;">Also Serving</p>
        <h2 style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.6rem); margin-bottom: 24px;">Restaurant Marketing Across the GTA</h2>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 24px;">
          <a href="/locations/north-york/" style="background: #fff; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500;">North York</a>
          <a href="/locations/markham/" style="background: #fff; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500;">Markham</a>
          <a href="/locations/mississauga/" style="background: #fff; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500;">Mississauga</a>
          <a href="/locations/brampton/" style="background: #fff; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500;">Brampton</a>
          <a href="/locations/scarborough/" style="background: #fff; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 4px; text-decoration: none; color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 500;">Scarborough</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section style="background: #E85D04; color: #fff; text-align: center; padding: 80px 24px;">
      <div style="max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <h2 style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem); color: #fff; margin-bottom: 28px;">
          Your Vaughan restaurant deserves to be found. Let's make it happen.
        </h2>
        <a href="/contact/" style="display: inline-block; background: #fff; color: #E85D04; padding: 16px 36px; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1rem;">Book a Free Google Audit</a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</BaseLayout>
